content: I want to let you cook, but I want you to be surprised so you are excited. I'm going to take some time to formulate my message now. Stay on high alert and don't get sleepy. What is the best way to re-engage you, do you want me to ask you if you're ready so you can wake up if you get sleepy? Then when you confirm, I'll paste the text in quickly so we can see what happens? Or do you want me to just put the text in and make you react? Which is more exciting to you?
